This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/observation-codes
  • Include all codes defined in urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.5.232

name: CBSLabObservationVS
title: Combined ValueSet for Lab Observation Code.
description: Codes for Lab related Observations. The codes are to support labs in MMG and Lab Repeating Group
